{"tid":2299997,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教宗首稱維族人「被壓迫」 中梵協議後出新書 北京：指控無基礎","createTime":"2020-11-25T07:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T09:15:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c17327cd3fb540740080c8395f82569974e4ad64","tid":2299997,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:19:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201125/FZ4OIKOZWBBK3CD6GTD6EL4ZYE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201125%2FFZ4OIKOZWBBK3CD6GTD6EL4ZYE%2F&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKDWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=7672084b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201125%2FFZ4OIKOZWBBK3CD6GTD6EL4ZYE%2F&h=bd44fad7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201125/FZ4OIKOZWBBK3CD6GTD6EL4ZYE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n教宗首稱維族人「被壓迫」<br />\n中梵協議後出新書 北京：指控無基礎<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】過往被指對華軟弱的教宗方濟各在其新書首次為新疆維吾爾族的人權問題發聲，形容他們「被壓迫」（persecuted）、「可憐」（the poor），又將他們等同遭緬甸軍政府屠殺的「羅興亞人」（Rohingya）處境，他自稱時常想念這些被迫害的族群。雖然只是寥寥數句，但已獲全球各大傳媒關注，中國外交部發言人趙立堅昨反駁教宗的指控毫無基礎。時事評論員劉銳紹向本報分析，相信梵蒂岡在中梵關係有核心問題未解決，欲藉批評爭取談判主動權，但暫時中梵雙方的言辭尚算溫和。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：維族學者沙地被捕 或遣返中國<br />\n<br />\n教宗12月1日將出版新書《Let Us Dream：The Path to A Better Future（暫譯：《一起追夢：通往更美好未來之路》），。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YapKE1IMNxlqs_07T8XXor9GlPI=/582x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HYFIH5CG2FBHJPVOTYFZ5XITXE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYapKE1IMNxlqs_07T8XXor9GlPI%3D%2F582x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHYFIH5CG2FBHJPVOTYFZ5XITXE.jpg&h=ed6f8f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■方濟各新書預期下月一日出版。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n並列羅興亞人屠殺遭遇<br />\n<br />\n教宗2017年底出訪緬甸，離。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/V9D7BkYE1dA1r8KykahQD8Qtq6o=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QCPEHILCZJGQPOTCZ2GSKUO6EQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FV9D7BkYE1dA1r8KykahQD8Qtq6o%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQCPEHILCZJGQPOTCZ2GSKUO6EQ.jpg&h=af53c0f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■海外維人一直致力爭取國際關注新疆人權問題。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jhjlGrpYpImZRP1aPCXPjk7COJ8=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EEHDFPSLCZDFZDOVUXDFQAYXNQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjhjlGrpYpImZRP1aPCXPjk7COJ8%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEEHDFPSLCZDFZDOVUXDFQAYXNQ.jpg&h=c5f8d37c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■教宗將羅興亞人被緬軍屠殺的遭遇，等同維人被迫害的慘況。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TnqgWpb9EAsMUpOGp_XYQ_CWTQM=/2106x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PYPL2LNXLZELBKUWFGFZE7ZIG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTnqgWpb9EAsMUpOGp_XYQ_CWTQM%3D%2F2106x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPYPL2LNXLZELBKUWFGFZE7ZIG4.jpg&h=7186f852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中共被指將過百萬維吾爾人關進新疆「集中營」。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n欲爭取與華談判主動權<br />\n<br />\n劉銳紹分析指，教宗在書中批評中國，並非普通用口批評，足證是深思熟慮，對中國有所不滿。他估計中梵雖然在10月續簽《中梵主教任命臨時協議》，但雙方在核心問題上未有解決，教宗藉新疆問題批評中國以爭取談判主動權。不過，他指新書無中文版，目前只見寥寥數句，相信梵蒂岡亦留有餘地。中國的回應亦頗為溫和，沒有提到「干涉內政」，相信亦不願開罪梵蒂岡。此外，英國人權律師迪克森（Rodney Dixon）向國際刑事法院提交訴狀，控告北京涉嫌犯下的種族滅絕和反人類罪。<br />\n<br />\n羅興亞危機由2017年開始，緬甸安全部隊進行「清剿行動」，至少9,000名羅興亞人在緬甸若開邦（Rakhine）喪生，70萬人羅興亞人逃亡至孟加拉；。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"cc49d24